<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=79585">www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=79585</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=garorm@thesteelwarrior>garorm</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.seretogis.org/files/linkables/ogrechief.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 34<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/24/03 4:29 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.seretogis.org/files/linkables/ogrechief.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: MB in POI</span><hr size=1> We have gotten the Behemoth down to 55% quickly with 25 people.  We are a guild on a pvp server with absolutely no emperor/seru/VT loot though.  I'm sure that a blue server could AM3/65-nuke the Behemoth down rather quickly with 30-40. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=339348" target="top">Veteran Garzok</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Overlord of  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.torrentvz.com" target="top">Torrent</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
